member.name: WRITE_THROUGH
member.summary: Specifies whether a storage device supports write-through caching.

member.name: WRITE_THROUGH.WriteThroughUnknown
member.summary: Indicates that no information is available about the write-through capabilities of the device.

member.name: WRITE_THROUGH.WriteThroughNotSupported
member.summary: Indicates that the device does not support write-through caching.

member.name: WRITE_THROUGH.WriteThroughSupported
member.summary: Indicates that the device supports write-through caching.
